  "commit_message": "rubocops/cask/url: add URL argument and string literal checks\n\nAddress review feedback:\n\nFlag `url` stanzas without a URL argument (e.g. only keyword\narguments). The Cask DSL silently treats these as getter calls and\ndiscards the keyword options. This also fixes a corrector crash on\nkeyword-only `url` stanzas, where the URL argument and the keyword hash\nare the same node and the keyword newline check built a reversed range.\n\nFlag non-string-literal URLs in Homebrew/cask. Dynamically generated\nUR",
